definitions.definition: The person or thing in the fifth position.

subdefinitions.definition: The fifth gear of a transmission .

definitions.definition: One of five equal parts of a whole: one-fifth .
A quantity of liquor equal to one-fifth of an American gallon , or, more commonly, 750 milliliters (that is, three quarters of a liter).
The musical interval between one note and another five scale degrees higher (the fifth note in a scale )
The fifth voice in a polyphonic melody.

main_definition: ( ellipsis or nominalization ) The person or thing in the fifth position.
